程序包 com.example.eventlink_qr_pro

类 AttendeeTest

java.lang.Object
com.example.eventlink_qr_pro.AttendeeTest
public class AttendeeTest extends Object
The AttendeeTest class conducts unit tests on the Attendee class, ensuring that all attendee attributes are correctly managed. These tests cover the setting and getting of various attendee properties, such as IDs, names, phone numbers, emails, check-in counts, e-tokens, image data, device IDs, and location data. Furthermore, it tests the functionality for enabling and disabling tracking for an attendee, as well as accurately finding and setting an attendee's location when permission is granted.
